                    <span>This book has been real help to me in "designing  implementation of  symbolic debugger" as my b.e. final year project. This book has been a  source of help in case of any problem i faced during my project.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A Good introductory book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
